0.1.2
=====
* Send an event out before opening inventory holder so other plugins have a
  chance to cancel it, for instance a container locking plugin

0.1.1
=====
* Add checking of permissions and a message to the player when they try to use a
  linked bookshelf without proper permissions.
* Added usage of MCStats
* Detect that the player is sneaking so shift clicking on a bookshelf lets you build

0.1.0
=====
* Initial version
